    <ol>
      <li class="first">
            
        <h3>Imagine</h3>
                
        <p>Decide where you want the Sun, Moon and Milky Way</p>        
        <div><img src="/sites/all/themes/photopills/images/how-it-works-1.jpg" alt="" /></div>
      </li>
      <li class="second">
            
        <h3>Plan</h3>
                
        <p>Easily calculate the exact date and time it happens</p>        <div><img src="/sites/all/themes/photopills/images/how-it-works-2.jpg" alt="" /></div>       
